{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-algorithm-scripting/where-do-i-belong","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-algorithm-scripting","demoType":null,"title":"Gde Pripadam","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Vratite najnizi indeks na koji vrednost (drugi argument) treba da bude ubacena u niz (prvi argument) nakon sto se niz sortira. Povratna vrednost treba da bude broj.</p>\n<p>Na primer, <code>getIndexToIns([1,2,3,4], 1.5)</code> treba da vrati <code>1</code> zato sto je veci od <code>1</code> (indeks 0), ali manji od <code>2</code> (indeks 1).</p>\n<p>Slicno tome, <code>getIndexToIns([20,3,5], 19)</code> treba da vrati <code>2</code> zato sto ce niz nakon sortiranja izgledati kao <code>[3,5,20]</code>, a <code>19</code> je manje od <code>20</code> (indeks 2) i vece od <code>5</code> (indeks 1).</p>\n</section>","id":"a24c1a4622e3c05097f71d67","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16094,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-algorithm-scripting/where-do-i-belong"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function getIndexToIns(arr, num) {\n  return num;\n}\n\ngetIndexToIns([40, 60], 50);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 35)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 35));"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 35)</code> treba da vrati <code>3</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 35), 3);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 30)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 30));"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 30)</code> treba da vrati <code>2</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 30), 2);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([40, 60], 50)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(getIndexToIns([40, 60], 50));"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([40, 60], 50)</code> treba da vrati <code>1</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([40, 60], 50), 1);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([3, 10, 5], 3)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(getIndexToIns([3, 10, 5], 3));"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([3, 10, 5], 3)</code> treba da vrati <code>0</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([3, 10, 5], 3), 0);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([5, 3, 20, 3], 5)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(getIndexToIns([5, 3, 20, 3], 5));"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([5, 3, 20, 3], 5)</code> treba da vrati <code>2</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([5, 3, 20, 3], 5), 2);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([2, 20, 10], 19)</code> treba da vrati <code>2</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([2, 20, 10], 19), 2);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([2, 20, 10], 19)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(getIndexToIns([2, 20, 10], 19));"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([2, 5, 10], 15)</code> treba da vrati <code>3</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([2, 5, 10], 15), 3);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([2, 5, 10], 15)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(getIndexToIns([2, 5, 10], 15));"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([], 1)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(getIndexToIns([], 1));"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([], 1)</code> treba da vrati <code>0</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([], 1), 0);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-algorithm-scripting","dashedName":"where-do-i-belong","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-algorithm-scripting","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-algorithm-scripting/mutations","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-algorithm-scripting/falsy-bouncer","id":"a24c1a4622e3c05097f71d67","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function chunkArrayInGroups(arr, size) {\n  let out = [];\n\n  for (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i += size) {\n    out.push(arr.slice(i, i + size));\n  }\n\n  return out;\n}\n\nchunkArrayInGroups(['a', 'b', 'c', 'd'], 2);","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-algorithm-scripting/where-do-i-belong"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}